High Yield Investor Savings AccountLooking for a good alternative for your cash? The FDIC-insured Schwab Bank High Yield Investor Savings® account offers a variable APY with no account minimums or monthly service fees.Ready to get started?Download an application.Learn more about our savings account.Home Loans—Provided by Quicken Loans®Purchase a HomeGet more loan options—and competitive rates—for home loans, and a quick closing through Schwab Bank's home loans program provided by Quicken Loans—the nation's largest online mortgage lender2 with over 31 years of home loan experience. Learn More 
Refinance Your Mortgage Refinance your home loan to shorten the length of your loan, or to lower your interest rate and reduce your monthly payments.   Learn More

Get a Home Equity Line of Credit (HELOC)Consolidate your higher-interest debt, finance home improvements, or make major purchases with our low-rate HELOC. It's an easy way to make the most of your home's equity. Learn More Ready to start the conversation?Get StartedCall 877-535-4021Mon.-Fri., 8 a.m.-9 p.m. ET; 8 a.m.-4 p.m. ET Securities Based LendingPledged Asset Line® (PAL)Whether you would like to renovate your existing property, invest in real estate, or expand your business, PAL gives you an immediate, flexible, non-purpose line of credit that leverages the value of your investments.Learn More Ready to open a PAL?Call 888-725-3630Mon.-Fri., 8:30 a.m.-8 p.m. ETOr visit your local branch to find out more.Community DevelopmentAt Charles Schwab Bank, we share your commitment to giving back to our communities. We demonstrate that commitment through a variety of community development efforts and activities that help serve the banking and credit needs of our entire community, including low- and moderate-income neighborhoods and individuals. Please see the Charles Schwab Bank CRA Strategic Plan for more details.





